import React from "react"
import cls from './SignUp.module.scss'

const Signup = () => {
   return (
      <form className={cls.root}>
         <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Login" 
         />
         <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="First Name" 
         />
         <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Second Name" 
         />
         <input 
            type="email" 
            placeholder="Email" 
         />
         <button type="submit">Login</button>
      </form>
   )
}

export default Signup
